pve-center (1.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * S3: decompose detail_panel.py (2509 lines) into detail_panel/ package.
  * Tab logic split into _host_tabs.py, _storage_tabs.py, _vm_tabs.py (controller classes).
  * Static helpers in _table_utils.py, worker management in _worker_manager.py.
  * Constants and TabIndex enum in _constants.py. DetailPanel is now a thin coordinator (~300 lines).
  * Public API unchanged — mainwindow.py sees zero difference.

