pve-center (1.0.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * R1/R2/R3: defensive race condition fixes — copy lists before iteration, atomic generation guard in soft_refresh.
  * M7: remove duplicate setStyleSheet/setDefaultAlignment on datacenter_summary (already set via _make_table).
